And if you want to tell Andy Davidson anything, write to me and I'll give it
to him. (As long as they aren't ideas for Worms that have any likeness to
something from Lemmings - and if they are, he'll come round to your place in
the night and insert a large joystick up your right nostril).

* And the words of the day are : 'Belisha beacon' *

- How to get REALLY weird landscapes...

If, when you click the right mouse button on the landscape generator, you
type in (without the quotes), "CJ TITS", a strange landscape will appear
before your eyes. (Avid viewers of Baywatch on TV will be in no doubt as
to why that was typed in!)
Try changing the 4th and 5th (i.e. T & I) letters and see what other shapes
you can make.

